## Figure 3 — Forest plot of effect sizes (η²p)

A forest-style plot makes the effect sizes visually obvious. Partial eta-squared conventions:

- 0.01 = small
- 0.06 = medium
- 0.14 = large

```{r viz-forest, fig.width=7.5, fig.height=4.5}
